るさいわね"]}, {"box": [426, 42, 449, 149], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["迷ったんだな"]}, {"box": [51, 40, 151, 167], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["おっかしいわね", "確かこっちで", "いいハズ", "なんだけどナ．．．"]}, {"box": [481, 216, 542, 316], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["あなたは", "黙ってついて", "来ればいいのっ"]}, {"box": [421, 710, 511, 797], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["どこへ", "行くの？", "２人とも"]}, {"box": [70, 826, 134, 952], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["遅かったわね", "葛城一尉！"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-047.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [662, 73, 690, 108], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["あ"]}, {"box": [425, 117, 466, 243], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["あんまり遅いから", "迎えに来たわ"]}, {"box": [350, 183, 417, 327], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["人手も時間もないん", "だから．．．グズグズ", "してるヒマないのよ"]}, {"box": [76, 60, 141, 187], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ごめ～～ん", "迷っちゃったのォ", "まだ不慣れでさ"]}, {"box": [501, 427, 542, 482], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["リツコ"]}, {"box": [666, 710, 739, 815], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["その子ね", "例の３人目の", "適任者って"]}, {"box": [404, 551, 454, 672], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["あ．．．初めまして", "碇シンジです"]}, {"box": [300, 584, 353, 708], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["なんだ！？", "適任者．．．って"]}, {"box": [212, 834, 257, 957], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あたしは技術一課", "Ｅ計画担当博士ー"]}, {"box": [161, 851, 188, 967], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["赤木リツコ"]}, {"box": [78, 904, 99, 985], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["よろしく"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-048.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [627, 69, 676, 174], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["いらっしゃい", "シンジ君"]}, {"box": [265, 37, 322, 145], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["見せたい", "もの．．．．．？"]}, {"box": [353, 134, 416, 287], "vertical": true, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["お父さんに会わせる前に", "見せたいものが", "あるの．．．"]}, {"box": [71, 216, 94, 279], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ですか"]}, {"box": [618, 311, 671, 417], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["司令！！"]}, {"box": [577, 661, 671, 812], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["進行ベクトル", "５度修正", "なおも進行中／"]}, {"box": [85, 462, 183, 632], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["使徒前進！", "強羅最終防衛線を", "突破！！"]}, {"box": [104, 718, 188, 939], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["予測目的地", "我第３新東京市／"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-049.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [665, 54, 740, 147], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["よし", "そういえば", "総員第一種", "戦闘配置だ"]}, {"box": [383, 53, 438, 144], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["冬月．．．", "あとを頼む"]}, {"box": [77, 60, 106, 114], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["ああ"]}, {"box": [461, 403, 496, 463], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["はっ"]}, {"box": [125, 508, 217, 615], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["３年ぶりの", "息子との", "対面か．．．"]}, {"box": [221, 657, 277, 764], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["総員第一種", "戦闘配置"]}, {"box": [137, 708, 186, 863], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["くり返す", "総員第一種戦闘配置"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-050.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [602, 53, 665, 224], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["対地迎撃戦", "初号機起動用意／／"]}, {"box": [250, 147, 298, 271], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ちょっと", "どういうこと？"]}, {"box": [76, 76, 209, 203], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["初号機は", "Ｂ型装備のまま", "現在冷却中！", "いつでも再起動", "できるわ"]}, {"box": [581, 536, 681, 678], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["そうじゃなくって", "レイにはもう", "無理なんじゃ", "ないの？"]}, {"box": [391, 695, 438, 814], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["パイロットは", "どうすんのよっ"]}, {"box": [66, 793, 147, 895], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["何考えてんの", "かしらしい", "司令は．．．"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-051.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [634, 61, 720, 212], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["それで", "ＮＮ地雷は使徒に", "効かなかったの？"]}, {"box": [460, 82, 585, 224], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ええ．．．", "表層部に", "ダメージを与えた", "だけ．．．．．．", "依然進行中よ"]}, {"box": [69, 79, 145, 220], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["やはり", "Ａ．Ｔブィールドを", "持ってるみたいね"]}, {"box": [640, 386, 710, 507], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["おまけに", "学習能力も", "ちゃんとあって"]}, {"box": [66, 368, 227, 574], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["外部からの遠隔操作", "ではなく", "プログラムによって動作", "する一種の知的巨大", "生命体とＭＡＧＩシステム", "は分析してるわ"]}, {"box": [682, 627, 707, 712], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["それって"]}, {"box": [426, 622, 455, 706], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["そう！！"]}, {"box": [273, 635, 329, 742], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["エヴァと", "いっしょ．．．"]}, {"box": [78, 628, 118, 699], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-052.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [561, 574, 592, 673], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["着いたわ"]}, {"box": [54, 668, 114, 774], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["暗いから", "気をつけて"]}, {"box": [295, 846, 318, 918], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ここよ"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-053.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [], "img_path": "EVA1-054.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [570, 75, 633, 160], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["これは"]}, {"box": [68, 723, 174, 868], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["さっき僕らを", "助けてくれた", "ロボット！？"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-055.jpg"}, {"version": 