{"box": [55, 844, 133, 980], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["今日来たばかりの", "この子には", "とても無理です！"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-058.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [619, 79, 674, 167], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["座って", "いればいい"]}, {"box": [309, 81, 374, 187], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["それ以上は", "望まん"]}, {"box": [109, 82, 264, 241], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["そのためには", "誰であれエヴァと", "わずかでもシンクロ", "可能な人間を", "乗せるしか", "方法はないのよ！"]}, {"box": [640, 235, 670, 326], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["もっ"]}, {"box": [372, 250, 397, 357], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["葛城一尉！"]}, {"box": [312, 261, 355, 380], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["今は使徒撃退が", "最優先事項よ"]}, {"box": [582, 555, 685, 696], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["それとも", "ほかにいい方法が", "あるとでも", "いうの"]}, {"box": [380, 653, 423, 746], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．"]}, {"box": [284, 609, 345, 738], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["さ．．．シンジ君", "こっちへ来て"]}, {"box": [58, 674, 96, 765], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-059.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [614, 57, 700, 153], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ぼ", "僕が．．"]}, {"box": [209, 48, 231, 172], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["これに乗って"]}, {"box": [120, 60, 175, 207], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["さっきの怪物と", "戦う．．．だって"]}, {"box": [93, 86, 109, 122], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["．．．？"]}, {"box": [579, 259, 641, 377], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ジョーダン", "だろ？"]}, {"box": [133, 305, 231, 474], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["そんなこと", "できるワケない", "じゃないか。", "！"]}, {"box": [648, 462, 677, 610], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["説明を受けろ"]}, {"box": [585, 502, 632, 625], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["おまえが", "いちばん適任だ"]}, {"box": [310, 682, 373, 783], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．なぜ", "僕なの？"]}, {"box": [72, 639, 200, 811], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ぜんぜん", "わかんない", "よ！！"]}, {"box": [533, 859, 597, 1006], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ほかの人間には", "無理なのだ"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-060.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [614, 78, 667, 239], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["今は", "わからなくてもいい"]}, {"box": [562, 132, 588, 252], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["出撃しろ！"]}, {"box": [198, 120, 231, 231], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["いやだ！"]}, {"box": [54, 159, 144, 343], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["できるワケないよっ", "こんなのに乗れる", "わけないだろ！！"]}, {"box": [650, 593, 704, 781], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["こんなことのために", "僕を呼んだのか？"]}, {"box": [578, 656, 636, 780], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["僕に死ねって", "ゆーのかよ"]}, {"box": [145, 600, 263, 709], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["おまえが", "やらなければ", "人類すべてが", "死滅すること", "になる"]}, {"box": [403, 881, 533, 1002], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["今まで", "ほったらかしに", "してたくせに", "虫がよすぎる", "じゃないか！！"]}, {"box": [64, 905, 138, 1043], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["人類の存亡が", "おまえの肩に", "かかっているのだ！！"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-061.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [147, 55, 221, 225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["なんて", "言われたって"]}, {"box": [82, 99, 136, 321], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["いやだよ！！"]}], "img_path": "EVA1-062.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 757, "img_height": 1057, "blocks": [{"box": [671, 78, 691, 145], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["そうか"]}, {"box": [269, 80, 324, 183], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["おまえなど", "必要ない"]}, {"box": [229, 14